data.description: Beautiful 5bedroom 2bath home that sits on large cul-de-sac lot in Newport. Split floor plan with jack-n-jill bathroom. Spacious living area with laminate flooring and brick fireplace. Large 5th bedroom with door to backyard, could be office or gameroom. Granite countertops in kitchen. Primary bathroom with granite countertops and walk in shower. New roof, HVAC system with dehumidifier installed in 2019. 12x24 shed with electricity.
